@project epsd2
@lang sux
@name epsd2/sux

@entry a [water] N
@bases a 
@form a /a #~
@sense N water
@end entry

@entry* a im šeŋ [rainwater] N
@parts a[water]N im[rain]N šeŋ[rain]V/i
@sense N rainwater
@end entry

@entry im [rain] N
@bases im
@sense N rain, rain storm
@end entry

@entry šeŋ [rain] V/i
@bases šeŋ₃
@sense V/i to rain
@end entry

